data.description: Welcome to your oasis that perfectly combines comfort, fun and more!  Nestled on a large corner lot, your remodeled home and a spacious workshop open the door to blending home and work balance with possible commercial opportunities.  The charm of covered porches invite you to relax and enjoy the surroundings.  Inside, an abundance of natural light graces every room, highlighting the neutral color palette that sets the tone for a timeless aesthetic. The heart of the home boasts a recently remodeled kitchen with quartz counters, stainless appliances and generous cabinets.  It seamlessly opens to the main living areas, fostering a flow ideal for daily living or entertaining.  There are two primary suites for extended family needs, adding comfort and privacy for all.  The remaining secondary bedrooms feature built-ins and a large closet.  All the restrooms have been remodeled or upgraded, providing modern amenities. There are many options in arranging furnishings in this home.  Need storage – you’ll find plenty of it here.     Step outside into the backyard oasis and prepare for relaxation or entertain like a pro!  The pristine heated pool and hot tub await, offering a refreshing escape during warm or cooler days. The adjacent resort-style cabana and multiple seating areas create a true haven, perfect for gatherings or peaceful solitude.  Beyond the main yard, the lot features cross-fencing, allowing for versatility in use and boasts both a greenhouse and dog mansion. The red-iron workshop with overhead door, measures an impressive 30x40, and is a dream space for creative projects or business endeavors. Rest easy knowing that recent updates, including HVAC, water heater, and a durable metal roof, provide peace of mind for years to come and energy efficiency. This property is not just a home; it's an opportunity to live, work, and play in a setting that effortlessly combines functionality with charm. Don't miss the chance to make this incredible property your own.
